title: Nyan Cat! v1.6
description:
BLAST into space on a brand new interstellar adventure guaranteed to blow you out of this universe! Nyan Cat! is the official mobile application of Nyan Cat designed by the creator of the brand new internet sensation, Nyan Cat!

Features:

- 4 exciting game modes
- 8 unique characters
- OpenFeint leaderboards and achievements
- 2 unique covers of the addicting music the Internet has come to love
- Surprising secrets

What's in this version:

- Added 3 new halloween-themed characters
- Better support for varied aspect ratios
- Bug fixes
